ive.org/web/20150518100656/http://www.atletico.com.br/profissional/lucas-pratto/ |title=Atl\u00e9tico Mineiro official profile}} {{in lang|pt}}\n* {{ESPN FC|109909<!-- /lucas-pratto -->}}\n* {{Soccerway|lucas-david-pratto/17657}}\n* [http://www.ogol.com.br/jogador.php?id=47630 Lucas Pratto profile] at OGol {{in lang|pt}}\n\n{{River Plate squad}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|title=Awards\n|bg=gold\n|fg=black\n|list1=\n{{Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n top scorers}}\n{{Argentine Footballer of the Year}}\n{{2015 Bola de Prata}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pratto, Lucas}}\n[[Category:Sportspeople from La Plata]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Argentine expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Argentine expatriate sportspeople in Brazil]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Boca Juniors footballers]]\n[[Category:Club Atl\u00e9tico Tigre footballers]]\n[[Category:Lyn Fotball players]]\n[[Category:Uni\u00f3n de Santa Fe footballers]]\n[[Category:Club Deportivo Universidad Cat\u00f3lica footballers]]\n[[Category:Genoa C.F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Club Atl\u00e9tico V\u00e9lez Sarsfield footballers]]\n[[Category:Clube Atl\u00e9tico Mineiro players]]\n[[Category:S\u00e3o Paulo FC players]]\n[[Category:River Plate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Brazil]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Chile]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Norway]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Italy]]\n[[Category:Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n players]]\n[[Category:Eliteserien players]]\n[[Category:Chilean Primera Divisi\u00f3n players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A players]]\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Argentina international footballers]]\n", "name_user": "Rupert1904", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eCareer statistics", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucas_Pratto"}
